4Geeks Academy offers a course in Applied Artificial Intelligence that is designed for professionals looking to utilize AI in their current roles. The course covers various aspects of AI, including generative AI, context, prompts, and models. It spans over six weeks and includes two live online classes per week. The class size is limited to a maximum of 12 students. Upon completion, students receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate recognized by multiple institutions. No previous experience is required to enroll in the course. For more information, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course. stop